				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%A1t/B%E1%BA%AFc-Giang-B%C3%A1i-th%C3%B4n-Thi%E1%BB%87u-H%C6%B0ng-t%E1%BB%B1-bi-k%C3%BD/poem-Rhfw2iSiBdZeuooTY5bYlg">Bắc Giang Bái thôn Thiệu Hưng tự bi ký - 北江沛村紹福寺碑記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Qu%C3%A1t/author-QI5swJgvY3VYWMQRAtFosg">Lê Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/%C4%90%E1%BB%99-Ch%E1%BA%BF-giang/poem-cn21oDZ6VwVbFyQAQto97g">Độ Chế giang - 渡制江</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Cao-B%C3%A1-Qu%C3%A1t/author-2eyz08Vw3mwjAHFJik43sA">Cao Bá Quát</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-d%E1%BA%A1-b%E1%BA%A5t-m%E1%BB%8B-ng%E1%BA%ABu-th%C3%A0nh/poem-4A9ED2n3AKGa7rAzHvlH1Q">Đông dạ bất mị ngẫu thành - 冬夜不寐偶成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-%C4%90%C3%ACnh-T%C3%BAc/author-DYGad0thHvgCxK3Szp1zVQ">Trần Đình Túc</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/H%E1%BB%99i-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Dng/poem-9KwY2aXw7vAPu5YHsPOnVw">Hội tường - 會祥</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-Hi%E1%BA%BFn-Gi%E1%BA%A3n/author--MNivfmhfmKdaENtm576XQ">Lê Hiến Giản</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/Kim-h%E1%BB%99-th%C3%A1n/poem-4AMefmYoEGv9ofjNb6bjUQ">Kim hộ thán - 金洿嘆</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%B9ng-Thi%E1%BB%87n-V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-ZzgazbvW_31Yn18OxsV6nA">Tùng Thiện Vương</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/Thu-ph%E1%BB%A5ng-qu%E1%BB%91c-tang-c%E1%BA%A3m-thu%E1%BA%ADt-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-erGZiuvEdLdysZ477DWtOQ">Thu phụng quốc tang cảm thuật kỳ 1 - 秋奉國喪感述其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Phan-Huy-%C3%8Dch/author-geNjG6kbAxWPLaqdF181sQ">Phan Huy Ích</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/T%E1%BB%91ng-kh%C3%A2m-ph%C3%A1i-%C4%91%E1%BB%91c-bi%E1%BB%87n-H%C6%B0ng-Y%C3%AAn-th%C3%A0nh-c%C3%B4ng-C%E1%BB%ADu-Y%C3%AAn-h%C3%A0-c%C3%B4ng-c%C3%B4ng-b%E1%BB%99-lang-trung-L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-h%E1%BB%93i-kinh/poem-fcLtFsn8sd0mAkNiaIL1Uw">Tống khâm phái đốc biện Hưng Yên thành công Cửu Yên hà công công bộ lang trung Lương hồi kinh - 送欽派督辨興安城工久安河工工部郎中梁回京</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90o%C3%A0n-Huy%C3%AAn/author-h3EvqeQvlQUxq2sceUWWYQ">Đoàn Huyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quy%E1%BA%BFn/T%E1%BB%B1-%C4%91i%E1%BA%BFu/poem-ZRHP1qz4lVkqBnCiDpmN5g">Tự điếu - 自吊</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Ng%E1%BB%8Dc-Quy%E1%BA%BFn/author-O3OAo7wTsvdoZtU7gOrz_g">Lương Ngọc Quyến</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/V%C3%A3n-ch%C3%AD-Tri%E1%BB%81u-T%C3%A2n-c%E1%BA%A3m-th%C3%A0nh/poem-wBUhglwoSRBr71U-dzofCg">Vãn chí Triều Tân cảm thành - 晚至瀍津感成</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A1i-Thu%E1%BA%ADn/author-l-NINz3JTJVTCX2aN0HlSQ">Thái Thuận</a>)<br></div>	</div>
